{"tid":561274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平昌冬奧】北韓啦啦隊戴上疑似金日成面具","createTime":"2018-02-15T00:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T01:42:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3daee5c21feb23827c6298f4912aa0e9b63028b8","tid":561274,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180212/640_71aa080ce283da22e843f4cd96d30a94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180212%2F640_71aa080ce283da22e843f4cd96d30a94.jpg&h=22635837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180212/640_aefa47252227ff796b04c88a6205daf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180212%2F640_aefa47252227ff796b04c88a6205daf3.jpg&h=a6752c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓平昌冬奧的觀眾席上，最受注目的就是北韓啦啦隊員。她們整齊劃一的動作，甚至被網友說比賽場上的選手還有看頭。不過北韓啦啦隊前日在看台上拿起一面男子形象的面具，立刻挑動南韓人的敏感神經。<br />\n媒體報導，前晚在兩韓女子冰球聯隊迎戰瑞士隊時，北韓啦啦隊員戴著面具為冰球選手們助威加油，這引起眾多猜疑，這男子面具難道是北韓前領導人金日成年輕時的肖像？對此，南韓統一部官員隔日澄清說，她們所戴的面具並不是指某個人，而是理想中的年輕帥氣男子。<br />\n除了面具爭議，這群啦啦隊成員的熱度其實已經蓋過平昌冬奧比賽本身。中國大陸媒體《中青報》說這群啦啦隊是「最美的觀眾」；《華爾街日報》與美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）則報導稱，她們讓全場觀眾觀賞到一場買票時未曾預期的娛樂表演。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180212/1296980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180212%2F1296980%2F&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldogHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=07ab515b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180212%2F1296980%2F&h=c6beee0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180212/1296980/</a>"},{"pid":"4f38be30e85deab2d21ab62b3cebc411bb20d056","tid":561274,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:17:05.000Z","msg":"估唔到共產黨同美國民主黨黨媒會臭味相投，齊撐北韓啦啦隊"},{"pid":"9bbab574b3fbf3506db07d106c69a7bf32577b89","tid":561274,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"金仔又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}